2. Legitimate creation date: The domain was created in March 2017, making it relatively new but still active today.

Overall, there is insufficient evidence to suggest that the domain "4im.us" is malicious. However, if you still have concerns about the domain, you can use the ICANN Whois Inaccuracy Complaint Form (https://www.icann.org/wicf/) to raise your concerns further. Remember to provide specific reasons why you believe the domain might be involved in malicious activity.
